<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA72">
<l>kaṇṭentai yeṉṟiṟaiñcik kaippaṇiyāṉ ceyyēṉē</l>
<l>laṇṭam peṟiṉu matuvēṇṭēṉ - ṟuṇṭañcēr</l>
<l>viṇṇāḷun tiṅkaḷāy mikkulaka mēḻiṉukkuṅ</l>
<l>kaṇṇāḷā vīteṉ karuttu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If I don’t act in order to humble myself, seeing [you and] bowing, saying “my father”,</l>
<l>even if I were to gain the cosmic egg, I would not want it, you with</l>
<l>the moon who rules heaven joined by a piece, you much husband of the seven</l>
<l>worlds. This is my intention.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
